<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">
I didn't get the AE root until level 45 - 46.  I have to say if I had to do it all over again I would get the AE root as soon as possible.  It really depends on if you want the pseudo-equal level pets first and get to mind 32 first.<P>At level 40, you can get to 30 body with 26 points into mind.  At level 43 you would finally get the last charm at mind spec 32.<P>If you get the level 32 charm first, you will have 23 in body.  You would get the AE root at 43.<P>It really depends on if you want the root or the pet first.  I probably would go with the root first and not worry about the pets for those 3 levels.  You'll being doing tanglers at that time and pets aren't as necessary (though helpful).<P>--------------------<P>Malachai Mindbender<BR>Sorcerer of Avalon<BR>Guinivere
