I just want to thank Quix76 for providing all the information I could possibly have wanted about sorcerers on his web page.  I went there when my sorc was a mighty level 14 and his information has allowed me to do the tanglers at level 37...THAT'S RIGHT, 37!!<BR>At 37 I had body at 30 and mind was about 21.  With a full group of all 40+ the resist rate gets cut down and they killed fast enough that the inferior mez didn't matter.  I go to his site almost every day now (don't tell my boss) just to check for any additional info. <P>My sorcerer, Chesh on Nimue, is now 30 body and 30 mind at level 42.  The other night when teh group found out I only had the 24 mez they were astounded.  I explained that if you use root first and then mez you get a much longer and easier CC time than overlapping a higher aoe mez.<P>Anyway, I attribute many of the compliments I receive at the tanglers to Quix's input and direction, and I'm grateful.
